title: EYL #153 Jim Jones, Styles P, 19 Keys, & Kenny Burns on Crypto, Health, & Technology
itunes:title: EYL #153 Jim Jones, Styles P, 19 Keys, & Kenny Burns on Crypto, Health, & Technology
description:
On episode 153, we’re sharing a highlight from Investfest, our conversation with four dynamic minds. Kenny Burns is the curator of culture, 19 Keys is one of the leading thought-leaders in the world, Styles P is one of the greatest lyricists of all time, a leading health advocate, and entrepreneur, and Jim Jones is a cultural icon who’s changing the face of Cryptocurrency and music technology. #cryptocurrency #jimjones #stylesp #19keys #kennyburns 


During this conversation we covered health, Cryptocurrency, NFT’s, virtual reality, the new business revolution of music, cultural currency, group economics and more.


EYL University: https://www.eyluniversity.com


Host IG: https://instagram.com/bankgreenwood?utm_medium=copy_link
